flowchart TD
  Browser["Browser"]

  subgraph Dev["Development run (npm run dev)"]
    Vite["Vite dev server (:3000)"]
    UI["React 19 + TypeScript UI<br/>src/App.tsx"]
    Agent["ResearchAgent<br/>src/services/researchAgent.ts"]
    Browser --> Vite --> UI --> Agent
  end

  API["FastAPI + Uvicorn<br/>backend/main.py"]
  Models["Pydantic request/response models<br/>backend/models.py"]
  Service["Research orchestrator<br/>backend/research_service.py"]
  Planner["Planner + Critic + Synthesizer<br/>backend/agents/"]
  Retrieval["Local corpus, chunking, hybrid retrieval<br/>backend/retrieval/"]
  Fetch["Page fetch + HTML text extraction<br/>backend/tools/fetch.py"]
  Eval["Dataset + eval runner<br/>backend/evals/"]
  Env[".env.local<br/>GEMINI_API_KEY"]
  Gemini["Google Gemini via google-genai"]
  Search["Google Search tool"]
  Corpus["Persisted run artifacts<br/>data/corpus/"]
  Render["Rendered output:<br/>summary, charts, evidence, gaps, activity log"]
  Dist["Built SPA assets<br/>dist/"]

  Agent -->|POST /api/research| API
  Vite -. proxies /api .-> API
  API --> Models
  API --> Service
  Env --> API
  Service --> Planner
  Planner --> Gemini
  Gemini --> Search
  Service --> Fetch
  Fetch --> Retrieval
  Service --> Retrieval
  Retrieval --> Corpus
  Retrieval --> Planner
  Eval -. runs orchestrator offline .-> Service
  Service -->|structured JSON report + steps| API
  API --> UI
  UI --> Render

  API -. when NODE_ENV=production .-> Dist
  Dist -.served by FastAPI .-> Browser
